052e2aa40ccee153f0b9934982fae74f9945e20f.query:
INSERT INTO users (id, slack_id, name, email)
    VALUES($1,$2,$3,$4)
    ON CONFLICT (slack_id)
        DO NOTHING;

899221ee4dfd9e73c4ae9828f50f7b8c7ee37fc3.query:
INSERT INTO back_blasts (id, ao, q, pax, date, bb_type)
    VALUES($1,$2,$3,$4,$5,$6)
    ON CONFLICT ON CONSTRAINT back_blasts_ao_date_bb_type_key
        DO NOTHING;

96b41fd06278d944f56fdfe98792ff6ce9d0f660.query:
INSERT INTO ao_list (id, name, days)
    VALUES($1,$2,$3)
    ON CONFLICT (name)
    DO NOTHING;

a82fab2c6d84945c51438aad27aa0a0b7729e844.query:
SELECT slack_id, name, email
        FROM users;

abca0edd4b11697c82c0d6c0dc9598ea3794db4d.query:
WITH list_view AS (
        SELECT
            ao,
            string_to_array(q, ',') as q,
            string_to_array(pax, ',') as pax,
            date,
            bb_type
        FROM back_blasts
    )
    
    SELECT ao, q as "q!", pax as "pax!", date, bb_type
    FROM list_view 
    WHERE pax @> array[$1] AND bb_type = 'backblast'
    ORDER BY date DESC;

db3dbdeb1dfacca1e233371423dba2c1237e9526.query:
SELECT ao, date
        FROM back_blasts
        WHERE bb_type = 'backblast' AND date >= $1
        ORDER BY date DESC;
